This CERN Open Hardware Licence version 2 (the “Licence”) governs the use, copying,
modification and distribution of hardware design documentation, and the manufacture
and distribution of products.

By exercising any rights granted under this Licence, You irrevocably accept these terms
and conditions.

This Licence is intended to apply to hardware design documentation, such as schematic
diagrams, circuit board layouts, mechanical drawings, and related documentation.

1. Definitions
“Documentation” means any design documentation, including but not limited to
schematics, PCB layouts, CAD files, netlists, bills of materials, and related files.
“Product” means any device or physical object that is manufactured using the
Documentation.
“You” means any natural or legal person exercising rights under this Licence.

2. Licence Grant
The Licensor hereby grants You a perpetual, worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free
licence to:
(a) use, reproduce, modify and distribute the Documentation;
(b) manufacture, use, sell and distribute Products.

3. Attribution
You must retain all copyright notices, licence notices, and attribution notices in the
Documentation.
You must provide appropriate attribution to the original Licensor in any distribution of
Documentation or Products, including a reference to the original project.

4. No Copyleft
You are not required to license modifications or derivative works under the same
Licence.
You may distribute modified Documentation or Products under any terms of Your choice,
provided that attribution is preserved as required by this Licence.

5. Disclaimer of Warranty
The Documentation and Products are provided “as is”, without warranty of any kind,
express or implied, including but not limited to warranties of merchantability, fitness for
a particular purpose, or non-infringement.

6. Limitation of Liability
In no event shall the Licensor be liable for any claim, damages, or other liability arising
from the use of the Documentation or Products.

7. Termination
This Licence shall terminate automatically if You fail to comply with its terms.
Upon termination, all rights granted under this Licence shall cease.

8. Governing Law
This Licence shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable
international copyright principles.

